==Translingual==

===Pronunciation===
/ eː / long close-mid front unrounded vowel: as a in game (not a diphthong), or é in café 

===Letter===
'''ए''' (e)

# A vowel of the [[Devanagari]] script.  It's [[matra]], used to modify the inherent vowel in a consonant is written &#x0947;.  For example the first consonant क with the matra looks like: के.

